Initial vaccine doses give a strong response, but over time, that protection can wane.

4
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:18,400
Studies show that booster doses can significantly enhance our immune response, especially against variants.

5
00:00:18,400 --> 00:00:22,000
Preliminary research suggests boosters could lead to longer-lasting immunity.

